Package: Certara.R
Title: Certara Pharmacometrics R Ecosystem and MCP Server
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: c(
      person("James", "Craig", email = "james.craig@certara.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Michael", "Tomashevskiy", email = "michael.tomashevskiy@certara.com", role = "aut"),
      person("Certara USA, Inc.", role = c("cph","fnd"))
      )
Description: Meta-package for the Certara pharmacometrics R ecosystem.
    Attaching 'Certara.R' loads the suite of Certara modeling, simulation,
    and reporting packages, and the package hosts the federated Certara
    Model Context Protocol (MCP) server that exposes knowledge-base and
    tool providers contributed by member packages to AI coding assistants.
URL: https://github.com/certara/R-Certara
BugReports: https://github.com/certara/R-Certara/issues
